<p>away from him lies the black entrance to a trench (the Support line) but he will never see it unless he stumbles upon it my chance, there is no sign on the surface of the ground that this is not a great white plain.<br/>Everywhere is this great strange white expanse seen but in another month the thaw and then back to the mud till the sun and Spring days dry up the Earth and prepare it for the Summer offensive.</p>
